rComments: Very helpful to students, quickly responds to them, offers office hours along with skype and facetime sessions to better understand what is going on. Really down to earth and understanding.
Les classes de méthodologie sont normalement ennuyants. Mais avec ce prof, c'était different. Bon prof qui connait très bien sa matière.

He is a really great prof as he was really flexible with the deadlines. His exams are very easy, most of the notes are posted online and we barely had to use the textbook. The final exam was take-home as well. He couldn't have made the theory class any better!

Amazing professor!!  He can be a little bit scattered and disorganized at times (class cancelled at the last minute, slow at returning assignments) but his lectures were always interesting and his love for teaching methodology really shows so he's easily forgiven for any flaws.  He's very approachable, friendly, and kind.

The best professor I have had so far! He managed to make a very dry topic extremely interesting. Extremely helpful and very clear expectations. I know everything I've learned this semester will help me in the future. His lectures were always entertaining and I consistently looked forward to this class even though it was at 8:30am!

This prof is remarquably versed in qualitative methodology. He managed to transform a potentialy very theoretical subject into a clear, practical and usefull course. He managed to adapt to the group needs. I wish all my prof would do that!

I didn't find this professor organized in the least. The final exam was supposed to be in class, and he switched it to take home without half the class knowing, then didn't post the questions for a long time. If you read the textbook it was easy to get an A+, but didn't find teaching at all remarkable.
Awesome! Clear expectations, very helpful, funny. Great course even if the subject was dry. Take his course no doubt
Très bon professeur. Exigeant mais toujours prêt à aider ses étudiants. Très drôle et aussi patient. Très recommandé
Excellent Professor. Funny, helpful, honest, the class material can be difficult, but he makes it interesting. I learned a lot.
Awesome prof! Made methodologies, which sucks, ok. His assignment was hard but he offered lots of help and was funny and honest with the class. Definitely take him for methodologies!

tres interessant comme professeur mais je trouve que il met pas mal de pieges pour l'examen et je trouve son assistant dur pour la correction des travaux,mais en general il est mieux que beaucoup de professeurs

I LOVE THIS MAN!! Seriously, this guy is like the best prof ever! Want an A? It's easy, just got  to every class and add your notes to the notes he has posed on Virtual Campus. He's down to earth, a pleasure to listen to, and a great professor!! He's seriously the best!

Great Prof! Highly recommended. No textbook, just weekly articles, mid term and final are take home. Easy Assignments, Easy A. Don't skip. Extremely helpful, peer reviewed an assignment for me and gave extensions. Excellent.

Professor is engaging, knowledgable, and down to earth. Presents course material in a manner conducive to various learning styles. In my opinion he is the epitome of what all professors should strive toward. I have come across only two others like him in my five years - I would highly recommend him.

Amazing Prof, takes dry subject matter and makes it interesting and relevant. Uses numerous aide to help facilitate learning such a videos and examples, and keep the class enjoyable with his humor and superb teaching style.  I wish all my Professors knew how to teach like this man, I highly recommend him.

Excellent! Ok, comme il l'a dit au début de la session: ce cours ne s,adresse pas au touriste qui souhaiteent des vacances! Mais les attentes sont claires. J'ai beaucoup aimé ce cours car il va me servir ailleurs. Très bon et surtout très pratique
i am seriously in love with him. wonderful, wonderful man.

Methodology was not my thing when I came into his class. Would not say it is now but I understand the importance of it. It changed the way I see and I read in all my other courses. Very good course and I recommend it since he makes things very clear to understand. Excellent prof!

Really interesting and easy to understand. Exams were straightforward - very close to the practice questions he goes over in class. He really knows his stuff and wants everyone to do well. Take anything you can with him :)
Excellent exemple de prof qui fait une différence. Merci!
Je ne peux pas imaginer comment plate ce cours aurait été sans lui. Super prof qui reussit presque à rendre une matière sèche intéressante. Il fera tout pour vous aidé. Recommandé A++.
Very nice professor, class was rather boring though. exams were open book, but very difficult

This prof is extremely entertaining and I highly recommend taking his course. I thought it would be boring but it has become my favorite class. He's always willing to help in any way he can and open to logical suggestions about the course. Always refreshing to have a prof who is genuinely passionate about their teaching, two thumbs WAY up for sure!
He's so adorable, teaches very well and is extremely helpful. I really recommend taking a class with him!

He kept things interesting with anecdotes and occasional videos, which made the 3 hour class go by quickly. He was also knowledgeable on the topic and very quick to respond to any e-mails and you could tell did his best to help every student out. There are no surprises, as he outlines everything you need to do well in the class.

In my opinion, he is an excellent teacher: enthusiastic, knowledgeable, and willing to help out anyone who needed it. For the exams, I would recommend studying both his notes and reading the book: his exams are mixes of the information in both. All in all, I really enjoyed this class and would recommend taking it with this professor!
He is an excellent prof.  If you go see him at his office hours.  He will helped you pass the course.  He is funny and make people in class laugh with him.  One of my professor of all time.
